---
By: Abhedananda
Locus:
  Page: 361
  Verse: 1
Tags:
  - Perseverance
---
Perfection means a state in which allyour senses and passions are
undercontrol and you are absolute master ofyour own self. Perfection does
notmean a realm, but a state of existence, alevel of enlarged consciousness
wherewe come into tune with the infinite.
